    <div class="field field-name-field-tags field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix"><div class="field-label">Tags</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/1">Drupal</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/taxonomy/term/4">Drupal 8</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/3">Drupal Planet</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p>There was a <a href="https://drupal.org/node/1952394">massive effort</a> recently to add a Configuration Translation UI to core, joining the existing Content Translation UI.</p>

<p>There were 27 people credited with contributing to this issue, which is incredible.</p>

<p>So incredible, that I thought it might have been a record. It turns out, it was a tie!</p>

